ContainedObjects.Name: Notecard
ContainedObjects.Description: At the start of each scenario, each investigator is dealt 2 secret objectives, they choose one. If they complete their secret objective at any time during the scenario, they add the card to their PERSONAL victory display.

ContainedObjects.Name: Notecard
ContainedObjects.Description: At the start of each scenario, investigators may collectively choose to draw a random ultimatum. These ultimatums significantly ramp up the difficulty of the game, but reward them should they overcome the challenges.
